    "Section 4 presents the findings of this systematic review and Sect. 5 draws the concluding remarks.",
    "Overview of SHAP and LIMEThe predictions of machine learning algorithms, particularly for medical diagnosis, can be disastrous if acted upon with blind faith.",
    "The models are evaluated based on accuracy metrics.",
    "Besides using accuracy metrics, inspecting each prediction and interpreting significant instances that lead to the decision is necessary [83].",
    "Such explanations for instances of individual predictions can lead to trusting the prediction [83]."
  ]
